# HTML conventions

## Page map (`index.html`)

- `#mainNav` — fixed navbar; links to `#portfolio`, `#about`
- `header` — profile image (`img/profile.png`), name, skills line
- `#portfolio` — three `.portfolio-item` tiles opening modals
- `#about` — two-column bio
- `footer` — contact, social links, tech icons (font-mfizz)
- `#portfolioModal1`–`3` — project detail modals at end of `<body>`

## Adding a portfolio project

1. Copy a `.col-sm-4.portfolio-item` block in `#portfolio`; update image and `href="#portfolioModalN"`.
2. Copy a `.portfolio-modal` block before the script tags; give it a unique `id`.
3. Place thumbnail under `img/portfolio/`.

## CDN assets

Styles and scripts load from CDNs in `<head>` and before `</body>`. Do not inline large libraries.

## Analytics

Google Analytics (`gtag`) in `<head>`; GTM noscript in `<body>`. Do not remove or duplicate tracking without user approval.

## Error pages

`403.html`, `404.html`, `50x.html` are standalone; keep styling consistent with the main theme where practical.
